---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy: GDPR and Swiss FDPA | Leone Consulting" 
  description="Privacy policy explaining how Leone Consulting collects, uses and retains personal data in compliance with GDPR and Swiss data protection regulations."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="py-32 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> February 16, 2026
        </p>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Leone Consulting<br/>
            Email: info@leoneconsulting.dev<br/>
            Website: leoneconsulting.dev
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            This document describes how we process personal data of users visiting the website 
            leoneconsulting.dev, in compliance with the General Data Protection Regulation 
            (GDPR EU 2016/679) and the Swiss Federal Data Protection Act (FDPA).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Data Collected and Purposes</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6">2.1 Browsing Data</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            During browsing, some technical data necessary for site functionality is automatically collected:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 my-4">
            <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Operating system</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
            <li>Referrer (source website)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Ensure proper site functioning, improve user experience, 
            anonymous aggregate statistics.<br/>
            <strong>Legal basis:</strong> Legitimate interest (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR).<br/>
            <strong>Retention:</strong> Maximum 26 months.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6">2.2 Voluntarily Provided Data (Contact/Booking Forms)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            When you fill out a contact or booking form, we collect:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 my-4">
            <li>First and last name</li>
            <li>Email</li>
            <li>Company (optional)</li>
            <li>Message/request</li>
            <li>Service of interest</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Purpose:</strong> Respond to your requests for information, quotes, consultations.<br/>
            <strong>Legal basis:</strong> Performance of pre-contractual measures at the data subject's 
            request (Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR) or explicit consent.<br/>
            <strong>Retention:</strong> 2 years from last interaction, or until consent is withdrawn.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-6">2.3 Cookies and Similar Technologies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We use the following types of cookies:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 my-4">
            <li><strong>Technical Cookies (necessary):</strong> Cookie preference management, user session. 
            Do not require consent.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics Cookies (optional):</strong> Anonymous site usage statistics. 
            Require consent.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            You can manage your preferences through the cookie banner or your browser settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Data Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Your data may be shared with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Vercel Inc. (USA) - servers for website hosting. 
            Data transferred outside EU with adequate safeguards (Standard Contractual Clauses).</li>
            <li><strong>Email Service:</strong> Email services for notification delivery (e.g., SendGrid, Resend). 
            Provider privacy policies apply.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Only if you consent, anonymous analytics services 
            (e.g., Plausible, Google Analytics with anonymized IP).</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            <strong>We do not sell or transfer your data to third parties for marketing purposes.</strong>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            In accordance with GDPR and Swiss FDPA, you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Obtain a copy of your personal data.</li>
            <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
            <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten").</li>
            <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Limit processing in certain circumstances.</li>
            <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format.</li>
            <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interest.</li>
            <li><strong>Withdraw consent:</strong> Withdraw consent at any time 
            (without affecting the lawfulness of processing based on consent before withdrawal).</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-6">
            To exercise your rights, contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@leoneconsulting.dev" 
            class="text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700">info@leoneconsulting.dev</a>
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the competent Supervisory Authority:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li><strong>Switzerland:</strong> Federal Data Protection and Information Commissioner (FDPIC) 
            - <a href="https://www.edoeb.admin.ch" target="_blank" rel="noopener" 
            class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">www.edoeb.admin.ch</a></li>
            <li><strong>EU/EEA:</strong> Supervisory Authority of your country of residence.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data 
            from unauthorized access, loss, destruction or alteration:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 my-4">
            <li>Encrypted HTTPS/TLS connection</li>
            <li>Secure servers with limited access</li>
            <li>Regular backups</li>
            <li>Anomalous activity monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. International Transfers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Some of our service providers (e.g., Vercel hosting) may be located outside the 
            European Economic Area (EEA) or Switzerland. In these cases, we ensure that transfers 
            take place with adequate safeguards through:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 my-4">
            <li>Standard Contractual Clauses (SCC) approved by the European Commission</li>
            <li>Adequacy decisions</li>
            <li>Privacy Shield Framework (where applicable)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Minors</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Our services are intended for individuals at least 18 years old. We do not knowingly 
            collect personal data from minors under 18. If you become aware that a minor has 
            provided us with personal data, contact us for immediate deletion.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. The "Last updated" date at the top 
            indicates when the most recent changes were made. We recommend reviewing this page 
            periodically for any changes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or the processing of your personal data, 
            you can contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            <strong>Leone Consulting</strong><br/>
            Email: <a href="mailto:info@leoneconsulting.dev" 
            class="text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700">info@leoneconsulting.dev</a><br/>
            Website: <a href="https://leoneconsulting.dev" 
            class="text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700">leoneconsulting.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
            <strong>Regulatory references:</strong>
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (GDPR)</li>
            <li>• Swiss Federal Data Protection Act (FDPA / DSG)</li>
            <li>• Data Protection Ordinance (DPO / DSV)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }
  
  .prose h3 {
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }
  
  .prose a {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
